This home has been approved for a "Live In" daycare center. It is not approved for a stand alone daycare. It is zoned M3 legal non-conforming. Please check the zoning and financing as it is a legal non-conforming use. The lot next door (1516 W Maryland) can be purchased with this house and would allow for more children to be kept at one time.  The home can also be a 3 bedroom 1 bath residence without much trouble.  All measurements are approximate and should be verified by Buyer or Buyer's agent.

To inquire about the property send an email to eickhoffpropertiesllc@gmail.com or call (812) 431-8278.
